1
00:00:00,140 --> 00:00:03,060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

2
00:00:03,060 --> 00:00:04,980
=Episode 8=

3
00:00:05,460 --> 00:00:06,900
Suisui,

4
00:00:07,100 --> 00:00:10,739
tomorrow we're going to
the palace banquet at Grandma's place.

5
00:00:10,740 --> 00:00:12,899
Really? Grandma is so thoughtful.

6
00:00:12,900 --> 00:00:15,579
Father, what kind of food
do they serve at palace banquets?

7
00:00:15,580 --> 00:00:17,500
Everything you drew is there.

8
00:00:18,140 --> 00:00:19,700
I see.

9
00:00:24,420 --> 00:00:26,900
Young Mistress, what's this?

10
00:00:27,060 --> 00:00:29,299
The biggest villain in the palace.

11
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:32,139
Tomorrow, I'll roast it

12
00:00:32,140 --> 00:00:33,900
and turn it into a dish.

13
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:36,080
(Chenhua Palace)

14
00:00:40,700 --> 00:00:42,440
Has the medicine been added?

15
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:45,659
(Chun'er, maid of Consort Shu)
Yes, Your Highness. It's already been added.

16
00:00:45,660 --> 00:00:47,480
This medicine is colorless and odorless.

17
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:50,000
Once she drinks it, within the time
it takes to finish a cup of tea,

18
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:52,580
her whole body will start itching,
and she won't be able to sit still.

19
00:00:55,620 --> 00:00:57,019
Mother,

20
00:00:57,020 --> 00:00:59,580
if that girl
embarrasses herself in public,

21
00:00:59,820 --> 00:01:04,619
then Xiao Heng won't escape
the blame for failing to discipline her.

22
00:01:04,620 --> 00:01:06,819
If she starts singing and dancing,

23
00:01:06,820 --> 00:01:08,820
I'll say she knows nothing
about palace etiquette

24
00:01:09,220 --> 00:01:11,940
and punish her by making her stay
in the palace to learn manners.

25
00:01:12,380 --> 00:01:15,900
Once Xiao Heng loses that girl,

26
00:01:16,060 --> 00:01:18,660
I'd like to see what else he can do.

27
00:01:19,780 --> 00:01:21,779
As expected of you, Mother.

28
00:01:21,780 --> 00:01:23,220
Brilliant.

29
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:25,300
Later, keep your mouth shut.

30
00:01:25,660 --> 00:01:27,139
Don't ruin my plan.

31
00:01:27,140 --> 00:01:28,379
Yes.

32
00:01:28,380 --> 00:01:30,420
I'll just sit back and enjoy the show.

33
00:01:35,260 --> 00:01:36,579
Wow.

34
00:01:36,580 --> 00:01:38,979
So this is Grandma's palace?

35
00:01:38,980 --> 00:01:41,020
It's huge!

36
00:01:51,140 --> 00:01:53,100
Greetings, Mother.

37
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:57,660
I specially prepared this banquet

38
00:01:57,940 --> 00:01:59,300
just for you two.

39
00:01:59,980 --> 00:02:02,860
Prince Jing, some time ago,

40
00:02:03,180 --> 00:02:05,460
I acquired an ancient painting
from the previous dynasty.

41
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,459
I heard you're skilled
in calligraphy and painting.

42
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:10,180
Go to the side hall
and help me examine it.

43
00:02:10,380 --> 00:02:13,420
Let Suisui stay here and eat first.

44
00:02:15,220 --> 00:02:16,539
Suisui.

45
00:02:16,540 --> 00:02:19,259
Father, it's okay.

46
00:02:19,260 --> 00:02:21,459
I'm not three anymore.

47
00:02:21,460 --> 00:02:22,759
It's not like

48
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:25,340
I'd tear down Grandma's palace.

49
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:28,379
Don't worry.

50
00:02:28,380 --> 00:02:30,900
I know my limits.

51
00:02:31,580 --> 00:02:33,019
If you stay here,

52
00:02:33,020 --> 00:02:35,220
you'll ruin my performance.

53
00:02:40,820 --> 00:02:43,180
Then I'll take my leave first.

54
00:02:58,100 --> 00:02:59,939
Grandma, I am hungry.

55
00:02:59,940 --> 00:03:02,459
Can I eat now?

56
00:03:02,460 --> 00:03:03,419
Go ahead.

57
00:03:03,420 --> 00:03:06,060
All of this is for you.

58
00:03:11,420 --> 00:03:12,540
Suisui,

59
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:15,340
have some tea first
to soothe your throat.

60
00:03:39,620 --> 00:03:40,659
Grandma,

61
00:03:40,660 --> 00:03:42,819
did this tea go bad?

62
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:45,420
Why does it smell strange?

63
00:03:46,580 --> 00:03:47,899
How could that be?

64
00:03:47,900 --> 00:03:50,819
This is freshly delivered
tribute tea from this year.

65
00:03:50,820 --> 00:03:52,220
How could it smell strange?

66
00:03:53,340 --> 00:03:54,339
Impossible.

67
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:56,139
My nose is very sensitive.

68
00:03:56,140 --> 00:03:58,540
Why doesn't Grandma smell it herself?

69
00:04:16,140 --> 00:04:17,580
Your Highness!

70
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:20,380
How dare you disrespect Mother!

71
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:22,380
I didn't mean it.

72
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:24,699
I just caught a cold.

73
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:27,099
Are you still going
to punish me for that?

74
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:28,220
You...

75
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:32,340
Forget it. Help me get changed.

76
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:33,699
Chun'er,

77
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:36,460
go bring Prince Jing
back to keep the princess company.

78
00:04:36,660 --> 00:04:37,619
Yes.

79
00:04:37,620 --> 00:04:39,700
Careful, Mother.

80
00:04:43,940 --> 00:04:46,100
My face!

81
00:04:46,580 --> 00:04:49,739
Hmph. Such a cheap trick,
and they thought they could fool me?

82
00:04:49,740 --> 00:04:52,299
Do they really think
I'm three years old?

83
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:54,500
I'm already five!

84
00:05:00,300 --> 00:05:00,859
Young Mistress,

85
00:05:00,860 --> 00:05:02,580
we caught a poisonous bug.

86
00:05:02,660 --> 00:05:05,540
It says it's going to be ground
into powder to poison your father.

87
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:16,199
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

88
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:20,039
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

89
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:23,559
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

90
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:26,520
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

91
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:31,039
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

92
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:34,800
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

93
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:38,199
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

94
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:42,240
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

95
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:51,519
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

96
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:55,159
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

97
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:58,879
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

98
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:02,519
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

99
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:06,199
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

100
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:08,119
♪Endlessly flowing♪

101
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:14,320
♪Good fortune♪
